        <title>Superconducting pairing correlations on a trapped-ion quantum computer</title>
            <categories>quant-ph cond-mat.str-el cond-mat.supr-con</categories>
            <comments>7+63 pages, 3+29 figures. v2: added an author, updated author contributions, competing interest, acknowledgement, updated references, fixed typos and added some diagrams to Supplementary Section S4, updated Supplementary Figure S27b, v3: corrected typo in author name</comments>
